<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>KosKu Solo</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --orange: #FF7A00;
    --orange-light: #FFF0E0;
    --orange-dark: #E06500;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --bg: #F7F8FA;
    --text: #1A1A2E;
    --text-2: #555770;
    --text-3: #9395A5;
    --border: #ECEEF2;
    --card: #FFFFFF;
    --green: #22C55E;
    --red: #EF4444;
    --blue: #3B82F6;
    --radius: 16px;
    --radius-sm: 10px;
    --shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
    --shadow-card: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);
  }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    background: #E8E8E8;
    display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  #app {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 430px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--bg);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .screen {
    position: absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%;
    display: none; flex-direction:column;
    overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: hidden;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }
  .screen.active { display: flex; }

  /* ===== SPLASH ===== */
  #screen-splash {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #FF7A00 0%, #FF9A3C 60%, #FFB347 100%);
    align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end;
    overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 60px;
  }
  .splash-bg-image {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center top; z-index: 1;
  }
  .splash-logo {
    width: 100px; height: 100px; background: white; border-radius: 28px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 48px;
  }
  .splash-title { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: white; letter-spacing: -1px; }
  .splash-tagline { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin: 10px 0 48px; text-align:center; padding: 0 40px; line-height:1.5; }
  .btn-splash {
    background: white; color: var(--orange); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
    border: none; border-radius: 50px; padding: 16px 60px; cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
  }
  .splash-wave { position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; }

  /* ===== ONBOARDING ===== */
  #screen-onboarding {
    background: white;
  }
  .onboard-slides { flex:1; overflow:hidden; position:relative; }
  .onboard-slide {
    position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    padding:40px 32px; transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .onboard-img { font-size: 100px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .onboard-title { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); text-align:center; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .onboard-desc { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-2); text-align:center; line-height:1.7; }
  .onboard-dots { display:flex; gap:8px; justify-content:center; padding: 16px; }
  .dot { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:4px; background:var(--border); transition:all 0.3s; }
  .dot.active { width:24px; background:var(--orange); }
  .onboard-btns { padding: 16px 24px 40px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--orange); color: white; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
    border: none; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; cursor: pointer; width:100%;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
  }
  .btn-primary:active { opacity:0.85; transform:scale(0.98); }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent; color: var(--orange); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
    border: 2px solid var(--orange); border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px; cursor: pointer; width:100%;
  }

  /* ===== LOGIN ===== */
  #screen-login { background: white; }
  .auth-header {
    padding: 60px 24px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #FF7A00, #FF9A3C);
    border-radius: 0 0 32px 32px; color: white;
  }
  .auth-logo { font-size:36px; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .auth-logo-img { width:72px; height:72px; border-radius:18px; margin-bottom:10px; box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
  .auth-title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .auth-subtitle { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.85; }
  .auth-form { padding: 32px 24px; flex:1; }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .form-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-2); margin-bottom: 7px; display:block; }
  .form-input {
    width:100%; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px; font-size: 15px; font-family: inherit; color: var(--text);
    background: var(--bg); transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .form-input:focus { outline:none; border-color: var(--orange); background:white; }
  .forgot-link { text-align:right; margin-top:-10px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .forgot-link a { color: var(--orange); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration:none; }
  .divider { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin: 20px 0; }
  .divider span { color:var(--text-3); font-size:13px; }
  .divider-line { flex:1; height:1px; background:var(--border); }
  .btn-google {
    width:100%; padding:14px; border:1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px;
    background:white; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text); cursor:pointer;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:10px;
  }
  .register-link { text-align:center; margin-top:24px; font-size:14px; color:var(--text-2); }
  .register-link a { color:var(--orange); font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; }

  /* ===== PILIH PERAN ===== */
  #screen-role { background: white; }
  .role-header { padding: 56px 24px 24px; }
  .back-btn { font-size:22px; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:24px; cursor:pointer; display:inline-block; }
  .role-title { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .role-sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-2); }
  .role-cards { padding: 16px 24px 40px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px; }
  .role-card {
    border: 2px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; padding: 24px;
    cursor:pointer; transition: all 0.2s; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px;
  }
  .role-card:hover, .role-card.selected { border-color:var(--orange); background:var(--orange-light); }
  .role-icon { font-size:42px; }
  .role-info h3 { font-size:17px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:5px; }
  .role-info p { font-size:13px; color:var(--text-2); }
  .role-arrow { margin-left:auto; font-size:20px; color:var(--text-3); }

  /* ===== SHARED COMPONENTS ===== */
  .top-bar {
    padding: 52px 20px 16px;
    background: white;
    position: sticky; top:0; z-index:100;
  }
  .bottom-nav {
    position: sticky; bottom:0; z-index:100;
    background: white; border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; padding: 8px 0 20px;
  }
  .nav-item {
    flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:4px;
    cursor:pointer; padding:6px 0;
  }
  .nav-icon { font-size:22px; }
  .nav-label { font-size:10px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-3); }
  .nav-item.active .nav-label { color:var(--orange); }
  .nav-item.active .nav-icon { filter: none; }
  .nav-dot {
    position:relative;
  }
  .nav-dot::after {
    content:''; position:absolute; top:-2px; right:-2px;
    width:8px; height:8px; background:var(--orange); border-radius:50%;
  }

  /* ===== DASHBOARD PENCARI ===== */
  #screen-dashboard { background: var(--bg); }
  .dash-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF7A00, #FF9A3C);
    padding: 52px 20px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .dash-top { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .dash-greeting h2 { font-size:20px; font-weight:800; color:white; }
  .dash-greeting p { font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-top:3px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; }
  .dash-actions { display:flex; gap:10px; }
  .dash-icon-btn {
    width:40px; height:40px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius:12px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:18px; cursor:pointer;
    position:relative;
  }
  .notif-badge {
    position:absolute; top:-4px; right:-4px; width:18px; height:18px;
    background:var(--red); border-radius:50%; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; color:white;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .search-overlay {
    margin: 0 20px; margin-top: -28px; position:relative; z-index:10;
  }
  .search-box {
    background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 14px 18px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap:12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }
  .search-box input {
    border:none; outline:none; flex:1; font-size:14px; font-family:inherit; color:var(--text);
    background:transparent;
  }
  .search-box input::placeholder { color:var(--text-3); }
  .dash-content { padding: 20px; }
  .section-header { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .section-title { font-size:17px; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); }
  .see-all { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--orange); cursor:pointer; }
  .category-scroll { display:flex; gap:10px; overflow-x:auto; padding-bottom:6px; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .category-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
  .cat-chip {
    flex-shrink:0; padding:8px 18px; border-radius:50px; font-size:13px; font-weight:600;
    border:1.5px solid var(--border); background:white; color:var(--text-2); cursor:pointer;
    transition:all 0.2s;
  }
  .cat-chip.active { background:var(--orange); color:white; border-color:var(--orange); }
  .banner-promo {
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, #1A1A2E, #2D2D4E);
    border-radius: 20px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; overflow:hidden; position:relative;
  }
  .banner-promo::before {
    content:''; position:absolute; right:-20px; top:-20px;
    width:120px; height:120px; background:rgba(255,122,0,0.15); border-radius:50%;
  }
  .promo-text h3 { font-size:18px; font-weight:800; color:white; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .promo-text p { font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
  .promo-badge {
    background: var(--orange); color:white; font-size:12px; font-weight:700;
    padding:6px 14px; border-radius:50px;
  }
  .kos-grid { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px; }
  .kos-card {
    background: white; border-radius: 18px; overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); cursor:pointer; transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .kos-card:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
  .kos-card-img {
    width:100%; height:160px; object-fit:cover; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE0C0,#FFB347);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:48px; position:relative;
  }
  .kos-badge {
    position:absolute; top:10px; left:10px; background:var(--orange);
    color:white; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:50px;
  }
  .fav-btn {
    position:absolute; top:10px; right:10px; width:32px; height:32px;
    background:white; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:16px; cursor:pointer; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  .kos-card-body { padding: 14px 16px; }
  .kos-name { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:5px; }
  .kos-addr { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-3); margin-bottom:10px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; }
  .kos-footer { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; }
  .kos-price { font-size:16px; font-weight:800; color:var(--orange); }
  .kos-price span { font-size:11px; font-weight:400; color:var(--text-3); }
  .kos-rating { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text); }

  /* ===== SEARCH / FILTER ===== */
  #screen-search { background: var(--bg); }
  .search-header { background:white; padding: 52px 20px 16px; }
  .search-header h2 { font-size:20px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .filter-bar { display:flex; gap:8px; overflow-x:auto; padding-bottom:4px; }
  .filter-bar::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
  .filter-chip {
    flex-shrink:0; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; padding:8px 14px;
    border:1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius:50px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600;
    background:white; color:var(--text-2); cursor:pointer;
  }
  .filter-chip.active { background:var(--orange-light); border-color:var(--orange); color:var(--orange); }
  .filter-panel {
    background: white; margin: 12px 16px; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .filter-section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .filter-section h4 { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:12px; }
  .price-range { display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; }
  .price-input {
    flex:1; padding:10px 12px; border:1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px;
    font-size:13px; font-family:inherit; color:var(--text); background:var(--bg);
  }
  .fasilitas-grid { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
  .fasil-chip {
    padding:7px 14px; border:1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius:50px;
    font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-2); cursor:pointer; background:white;
  }
  .fasil-chip.active { background:var(--orange-light); border-color:var(--orange); color:var(--orange); }
  .filter-actions { display:flex; gap:10px; padding: 0 16px 20px; }
  .btn-secondary {
    flex:1; padding:14px; border:2px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px;
    font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text-2); background:white; cursor:pointer;
  }
  .btn-primary-flex { flex:2; }
  .search-results { padding: 16px; }
  .results-count { font-size:13px; color:var(--text-2); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .kos-list-card {
    background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:14px; margin-bottom:12px;
    display:flex; gap:14px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); cursor:pointer;
  }
  .kos-list-img {
    width:100px; height:85px; border-radius:12px; flex-shrink:0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE0C0,#FFB347);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:36px;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .kos-list-img img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .kos-list-info { flex:1; min-width:0; }
  .kos-list-name { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:4px; }
  .kos-list-addr { font-size:11px; color:var(--text-3); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .kos-list-price { font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:var(--orange); margin-bottom:4px; }
  .kos-list-footer { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; }

  /* ===== DETAIL KOS ===== */
  #screen-detail { background: white; }
  .detail-header { position:relative; }
  .detail-photos {
    width:100%; height:260px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE0C0,#FF9A3C);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:72px;
    position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .detail-photos img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .detail-back {
    position:absolute; top:52px; left:16px; width:40px; height:40px;
    background:white; border-radius:12px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:20px; cursor:pointer; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  .photo-count {
    position:absolute; bottom:14px; right:14px; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
    color:white; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding:5px 12px; border-radius:50px;
  }
  .detail-body { padding: 20px; }
  .detail-name { font-size:22px; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .detail-addr { font-size:14px; color:var(--text-2); display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .detail-meta { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .detail-price { font-size:24px; font-weight:800; color:var(--orange); }
  .detail-price span { font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:var(--text-3); }
  .detail-rating { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px; }
  .stars { color:#FBBF24; font-size:14px; }
  .rating-val { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .rating-count { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-3); }
  .section-divider { height:8px; background:var(--bg); margin: 0 -20px 18px; }
  .detail-section-title { font-size:17px; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .fasil-grid { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .fasil-tag {
    padding:8px 14px; background:var(--orange-light); border-radius:50px;
    font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--orange); display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;
  }
  .rules-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
  .rule-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-size:14px; color:var(--text-2); }
  .rule-dot { width:8px; height:8px; background:var(--orange); border-radius:50%; flex-shrink:0; }
  .detail-owner {
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; padding: 14px;
    background:var(--bg); border-radius:14px; margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .owner-avatar {
    width:48px; height:48px; background:var(--orange); border-radius:14px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:22px; color:white;
  }
  .owner-name { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .owner-role { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-3); }
  .detail-actions {
    position:sticky; bottom:0; background:white; padding:16px 20px 30px;
    border-top:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; gap:12px;
  }
  .btn-chat {
    flex:1; padding:15px; border:2px solid var(--orange); border-radius:14px;
    font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--orange); background:white; cursor:pointer;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px;
  }
  .btn-booking {
    flex:2; padding:15px; background:var(--orange); border:none; border-radius:14px;
    font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:white; cursor:pointer;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px;
  }

  /* ===== MAPS ===== */
  #screen-maps { background: var(--bg); }
  .maps-header {
    background:white; padding: 52px 20px 16px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px;
  }
  .maps-container {
    margin:12px 16px; border-radius:20px; overflow:hidden;
    height:320px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#E8F4FD,#DBEAFE);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-direction:column;
    position:relative; box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .map-placeholder { font-size:60px; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .map-label { font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); }
  .map-pin {
    position:absolute; top:40%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
    background:var(--orange); color:white; font-size:12px; font-weight:700;
    padding:6px 12px; border-radius:50px; white-space:nowrap;
    box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(255,122,0,0.4);
  }
  .map-pin::after {
    content:''; position:absolute; bottom:-8px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%);
    border:4px solid transparent; border-top:8px solid var(--orange);
  }
  .map-info { padding: 16px; }
  .map-detail-card {
    background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:16px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow); margin-bottom:12px;
  }
  .map-kos-name { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:6px; }
  .map-kos-addr { font-size:13px; color:var(--text-2); margin-bottom:12px; display:flex; gap:6px; }
  .map-stats { display:flex; gap:16px; }
  .map-stat { text-align:center; }
  .map-stat-val { font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:var(--orange); }
  .map-stat-label { font-size:11px; color:var(--text-3); }
  .map-actions { display:flex; gap:10px; }

  /* ===== BOOKING ===== */
  #screen-booking { background: var(--bg); }
  .booking-header { background:white; padding: 52px 20px 16px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }
  .booking-body { padding: 16px; }
  .booking-kos-card {
    background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:14px; display:flex; gap:12px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow); margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .booking-kos-img {
    width:70px; height:65px; border-radius:12px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE0C0,#FF9A3C);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:28px; flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .booking-kos-name { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .booking-kos-addr { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-3); margin-top:3px; }
  .booking-form { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:18px; margin-bottom:16px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
  .booking-form h3 { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .select-input {
    width:100%; padding:14px 16px; border:1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px;
    font-size:15px; font-family:inherit; color:var(--text); background:var(--bg);
    appearance:none; cursor:pointer;
  }
  .summary-card { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:18px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .summary-card h3 { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .summary-row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:10px; font-size:14px; }
  .summary-row .label { color:var(--text-2); }
  .summary-row .value { font-weight:600; color:var(--text); }
  .summary-divider { height:1px; background:var(--border); margin:12px 0; }
  .summary-total { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; }
  .summary-total .label { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .summary-total .value { font-size:17px; font-weight:800; color:var(--orange); }
  .booking-footer { padding: 0 16px 30px; }

  /* ===== PAYMENT ===== */
  #screen-payment { background: var(--bg); }
  .payment-header { background:white; padding: 52px 20px 16px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }
  .payment-body { padding: 16px; }
  .payment-detail-card { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:18px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .payment-detail-card h3 { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .payment-method { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:18px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .method-title { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .method-option {
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; padding:12px 0;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); cursor:pointer;
  }
  .method-option:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .method-icon { font-size:24px; width:40px; text-align:center; }
  .method-name { font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text); flex:1; }
  .method-radio {
    width:20px; height:20px; border:2px solid var(--border); border-radius:50%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .method-radio.selected { border-color:var(--orange); background:var(--orange); }
  .method-radio.selected::after { content:''; width:8px; height:8px; background:white; border-radius:50%; }

  /* ===== RIWAYAT ===== */
  #screen-riwayat { background: var(--bg); }
  .tab-bar { display:flex; border-bottom:2px solid var(--border); background:white; }
  .tab-item {
    flex:1; padding:14px; text-align:center; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-3);
    cursor:pointer; border-bottom:2px solid transparent; margin-bottom:-2px; transition:all 0.2s;
  }
  .tab-item.active { color:var(--orange); border-bottom-color:var(--orange); }
  .riwayat-list { padding:16px; }
  .riwayat-card { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:12px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
  .riwayat-head { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .riwayat-img { width:56px; height:52px; border-radius:10px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE0C0,#FF9A3C); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:22px; }
  .riwayat-name { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .riwayat-kamar { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-3); margin-top:2px; }
  .status-badge {
    margin-left:auto; padding:5px 12px; border-radius:50px; font-size:11px; font-weight:700;
  }
  .status-active { background:#DCFCE7; color:#16A34A; }
  .status-done { background:#F1F5F9; color:#64748B; }
  .status-cancel { background:#FEE2E2; color:#DC2626; }
  .riwayat-detail { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding-top:12px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); }
  .riwayat-info p { font-size:11px; color:var(--text-3); margin-bottom:2px; }
  .riwayat-info span { font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }

  /* ===== CHAT ===== */
  #screen-chat { background: var(--bg); }
  .chat-list-item {
    display:flex; gap:12px; padding:14px 20px; cursor:pointer;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); background:white; align-items:center;
  }
  .chat-list-item:active { background:var(--bg); }
  .chat-header { background:white; padding: 52px 20px 14px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; }
  .chat-avatar { width:44px; height:44px; background:var(--orange); border-radius:13px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:20px; }
  .chat-name { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .chat-status { font-size:12px; color:var(--green); font-weight:600; }
  .chat-messages { flex:1; padding:16px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; overflow-y:auto; }
  .msg-bubble { max-width:75%; }
  .msg-bubble.received { align-self:flex-start; }
  .msg-bubble.sent { align-self:flex-end; }
  .bubble {
    padding:12px 16px; border-radius:18px; font-size:14px; line-height:1.5;
  }
  .msg-bubble.received .bubble { background:white; color:var(--text); border-bottom-left-radius:4px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
  .msg-bubble.sent .bubble { background:var(--orange); color:white; border-bottom-right-radius:4px; }
  .msg-time { font-size:10px; color:var(--text-3); margin-top:4px; }
  .msg-bubble.sent .msg-time { text-align:right; }
  .chat-input-bar {
    background:white; padding:12px 16px 28px; border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-end;
  }
  .chat-input-box {
    flex:1; background:var(--bg); border-radius:20px; padding:12px 16px;
    font-size:14px; font-family:inherit; border:none; outline:none; resize:none; max-height:100px;
  }
  .chat-send-btn {
    width:44px; height:44px; background:var(--orange); border-radius:13px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:20px; cursor:pointer; flex-shrink:0;
  }

  /* ===== FAVORIT ===== */
  #screen-favorit { background: var(--bg); }
  .favorit-body { padding:16px; }

  /* ===== PROFIL ===== */
  #screen-profil { background: var(--bg); }
  .profil-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF7A00, #FF9A3C);
    padding: 60px 24px 28px; text-align:center;
  }
  .profil-avatar {
    width:80px; height:80px; background:white; border-radius:24px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:36px;
    margin:0 auto 14px; box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  .profil-name { font-size:20px; font-weight:800; color:white; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .profil-email { font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
  .profil-body { padding:20px; }
  .profil-menu { background:white; border-radius:18px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
  .menu-item {
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; padding:17px 18px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); cursor:pointer; transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .menu-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .menu-item:active { background:var(--bg); }
  .menu-item-icon { font-size:22px; width:36px; text-align:center; }
  .menu-item-label { font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text); flex:1; }
  .menu-arrow { color:var(--text-3); font-size:16px; }
  .menu-item.danger .menu-item-label { color:var(--red); }

  /* ===== OWNER DASHBOARD ===== */
  #screen-owner { background: var(--bg); }
  .owner-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1A2E, #2D2D4E);
    padding: 52px 20px 24px;
  }
  .owner-greet { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .owner-greet h2 { font-size:20px; font-weight:800; color:white; }
  .owner-greet p { font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top:3px; }
  .stats-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; }
  .stat-card {
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius:14px; padding:14px; text-align:center;
  }
  .stat-val { font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:white; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .stat-label { font-size:11px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-weight:600; }
  .stat-card.highlight { background:var(--orange); }
  .owner-menu-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px; padding:16px; }
  .owner-menu-card {
    background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:18px; text-align:center;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow); cursor:pointer; transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .owner-menu-card:active { transform:scale(0.96); }
  .owner-menu-icon { font-size:32px; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .owner-menu-label { font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .owner-menu-badge { margin-top:4px; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:var(--orange); }

  /* ===== BOOKING MASUK (OWNER) ===== */
  #screen-booking-masuk { background: var(--bg); }
  .booking-req-card {
    background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:12px; box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .booking-req-head { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .req-avatar { width:48px; height:48px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#E0E7FF,#C7D2FE); border-radius:14px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:22px; }
  .req-name { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .req-time { font-size:11px; color:var(--text-3); }
  .req-info { display:flex; gap:16px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .req-info-item p { font-size:11px; color:var(--text-3); margin-bottom:2px; }
  .req-info-item span { font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); }
  .req-actions { display:flex; gap:8px; }
  .btn-terima { flex:1; padding:10px; background:var(--green); border:none; border-radius:10px; color:white; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; }
  .btn-tolak { flex:1; padding:10px; background:var(--red); border:none; border-radius:10px; color:white; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; }
  .btn-chat-req { padding:10px 16px; background:var(--bg); border:none; border-radius:10px; color:var(--text-2); font-size:13px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; }

  /* ===== KEUANGAN OWNER ===== */
  #screen-keuangan { background: var(--bg); }
  .keu-header { background:white; padding:52px 20px 16px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }
  .keu-body { padding:16px; }
  .income-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF7A00, #FF9A3C);
    border-radius:20px; padding:20px; margin-bottom:16px; color:white;
  }
  .income-label { font-size:13px; opacity:0.8; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .income-val { font-size:32px; font-weight:800; }
  .income-period { font-size:12px; opacity:0.7; margin-top:4px; }
  .income-tabs { display:flex; gap:8px; margin-top:16px; }
  .income-tab {
    padding:6px 14px; border-radius:50px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color:white;
  }
  .income-tab.active { background:white; color:var(--orange); }
  .chart-card { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:16px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .chart-title { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .bar-chart { display:flex; align-items:flex-end; gap:6px; height:120px; }
  .bar-wrap { flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:6px; }
  .bar { width:100%; border-radius:6px 6px 0 0; background:var(--orange-light); min-height:10px; transition:height 0.5s ease; }
  .bar.highlight { background:var(--orange); }
  .bar-label { font-size:9px; color:var(--text-3); font-weight:600; }
  .bar-val { font-size:8px; color:var(--text-3); }

  /* ===== NOTIFIKASI ===== */
  #screen-notif { background: var(--bg); }
  .notif-list { padding:16px; }
  .notif-item {
    background:white; border-radius:14px; padding:14px; margin-bottom:10px;
    display:flex; gap:12px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); cursor:pointer;
  }
  .notif-item.unread { border-left:3px solid var(--orange); }
  .notif-icon { font-size:28px; width:44px; height:44px; background:var(--orange-light); border-radius:12px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }
  .notif-text h4 { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:3px; }
  .notif-text p { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-2); line-height:1.5; }
  .notif-time { font-size:11px; color:var(--text-3); margin-top:4px; }

  /* ===== STREET VIEW ===== */
  #screen-streetview { background: #1A1A2E; }
  .sv-header { padding:52px 20px 14px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; }
  .sv-title { font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:white; }
  .sv-container {
    margin:0 16px; border-radius:20px; overflow:hidden; height:340px;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#87CEEB 0%, #87CEEB 60%, #9E9E9E 60%, #757575 100%);
    position:relative; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .sv-road {
    position:absolute; bottom:0; width:100%; height:40%;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#616161,#424242);
    display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:flex-start; padding-top:20px;
  }
  .sv-road::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); width:4px; height:100%; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
  .sv-building { position:absolute; bottom:40%; font-size:80px; }
  .sv-label-box {
    position:absolute; top:14px; left:14px; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.65);
    padding:8px 14px; border-radius:10px;
  }
  .sv-label-box p { font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
  .sv-label-box h4 { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:white; }
  .sv-controls {
    position:absolute; bottom:14px; right:14px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px;
  }
  .sv-btn {
    width:36px; height:36px; background:white; border-radius:10px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:16px; cursor:pointer;
    box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .sv-info { padding:16px; }
  .sv-info-card { background:#2D2D4E; border-radius:16px; padding:16px; }
  .sv-info-title { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:white; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .sv-info-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
  .sv-info-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }

  /* ===== TAMBAH KOS ===== */
  #screen-tambah-kos { background:var(--bg); }
  .tambah-header { background:white; padding:52px 20px 16px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }
  .tambah-body { padding:16px; }
  .form-card { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:18px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .form-card h3 { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .jenis-grid { display:flex; gap:8px; }
  .jenis-btn { flex:1; padding:10px; border:1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-2); background:white; cursor:pointer; text-align:center; }
  .jenis-btn.active { border-color:var(--orange); background:var(--orange-light); color:var(--orange); }
  .photo-upload {
    border:2px dashed var(--border); border-radius:14px; height:120px;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    cursor:pointer; transition:border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .photo-upload:hover { border-color:var(--orange); }
  .photo-upload-icon { font-size:32px; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .photo-upload-text { font-size:13px; color:var(--text-3); font-weight:600; }
  textarea.form-input { min-height:90px; resize:none; }

  /* ===== KELOLA KOS LIST ===== */
  .kk-card { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:14px; margin-bottom:12px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
  .kk-card-top { display:flex; gap:12px; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .kk-img { width:64px; height:60px; border-radius:12px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE0C0,#FF9A3C); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:26px; flex-shrink:0; }
  .kk-name { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:3px; }
  .kk-addr { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-3); margin-bottom:4px; }
  .kk-meta { font-size:12px; color:var(--orange); font-weight:700; }
  .kk-status-toggle {
    margin-left:auto; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:50px; cursor:pointer; height:fit-content;
  }
  .kk-status-aktif { background:#DCFCE7; color:#16A34A; }
  .kk-status-nonaktif { background:#F1F5F9; color:#64748B; }
  .kk-actions { display:flex; gap:8px; padding-top:10px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); }
  .kk-btn { flex:1; padding:9px; border:none; border-radius:10px; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; text-align:center; }
  .kk-btn-edit { background:var(--orange-light); color:var(--orange); }
  .kk-btn-delete { background:#FEE2E2; color:var(--red); }

  /* ===== SUCCESS SCREEN ===== */
  #screen-success { background:white; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }
  .success-icon { font-size:80px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .success-title { font-size:24px; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .success-desc { font-size:14px; color:var(--text-2); text-align:center; padding:0 32px; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:40px; }
  .success-card {
    background:var(--bg); border-radius:16px; padding:18px; margin:0 24px 32px; width:calc(100% - 48px);
  }

  /* ===== REGISTER ===== */
  #screen-register { background: white; }

  /* === Utilities === */
  .text-orange { color:var(--orange); }
  .fw-700 { font-weight:700; }
  .mt-4 { margin-top:4px; }
  .mb-0 { margin-bottom:0; }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(12px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
  .screen.active { animation: fadeIn 0.25s ease; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{transform:scale(1);} 50%{transform:scale(1.05);} }
  .pulse { animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">

  <!-- ===== SPLASH SCREEN ===== -->
  <div id="screen-splash" class="screen active">
    <img class="splash-bg-image" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="KosKu Solo">
    <button class="btn-splash" onclick="showOnboarding()">Mulai</button>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== ONBOARDING ===== -->
  <div id="screen-onboarding" class="screen">
    <div class="onboard-slides" id="onboardSlides">
      <div class="onboard-slide" id="slide-0">
        <div class="onboard-img">🔍</div>
        <div class="onboard-title">Cari Kos Terbaik di Solo</div>
        <div class="onboard-desc">Temukan ribuan pilihan kos sesuai kebutuhan Anda, mulai dari kos putra, putri, hingga eksklusif.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="onboard-slide" id="slide-1" style="transform:translateX(100%)">
        <div class="onboard-img">🗺️</div>
        <div class="onboard-title">Lihat Lokasi Secara Akurat</div>
        <div class="onboard-desc">Gunakan Google Maps dan Street View untuk melihat lokasi kos secara real dan detail.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="onboard-slide" id="slide-2" style="transform:translateX(200%)">
        <div class="onboard-img">📱</div>
        <div class="onboard-title">Booking Langsung dari Aplikasi</div>
        <div class="onboard-desc">Pesan kamar dan lakukan pembayaran dengan aman hanya dalam beberapa langkah mudah.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="onboard-dots" id="onboardDots">
      <div class="dot active"></div>
      <div class="dot"></div>
      <div class="dot"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="onboard-btns">
      <button class="btn-primary" id="onboardNextBtn" onclick="nextSlide()">Selanjutnya</button>
      <button class="btn-outline" onclick="showLogin()">Lewati</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== LOGIN ===== -->
  <div id="screen-login" class="screen">
    <div class="auth-header">
      <img class="auth-logo-img" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="KosKu Solo">
      <div class="auth-title">Selamat Datang 👋</div>
      <div class="auth-subtitle">Masuk untuk melanjutkan</div>
    </div>
    <div class="auth-form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">Email / Nomor HP</label>
        <input class="form-input" id="loginIdentifier" type="text" placeholder="Masukkan email atau no. HP">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">Password</label>
